- Hm?

8
00:02:11,382 --> 00:02:14,093
[Steve] Oh... yeah.

9
00:02:14,302 --> 00:02:16,053
That's beautiful.

10
00:02:17,888 --> 00:02:19,473
[Steve]
They were flying so many planes,

11
