18
00:02:44,832 --> 00:02:46,709
[Speaking Spanish]
Let's get down!

19
00:02:46,959 --> 00:02:49,545
[All cheering]

20
00:02:50,921 --> 00:02:54,675
[Steve] The problem was
no longer demand... it was supply.

21
