- What?

52
00:04:53,085 --> 00:04:54,503
It's my dog.

53
00:05:02,803 --> 00:05:04,096
[Gustavo] What happened?

54
00:05:04,180 --> 00:05:06,599
[Gacha]
You want to know what happened? Go look.

55
00:05:08,058 --> 00:05:09,268
