The ochoas are soft.

135
00:09:43,584 --> 00:09:44,918
Wait a second.

136
00:09:46,044 --> 00:09:47,963
What about Pablo Escobar?

137
00:09:48,046 --> 00:09:49,923
[Steve]
I know what you're thinking.

138
00:09:50,007 --> 00:09:52,801
